                    "@type": "Answer",
                    text: "Efficient for its class. In a Colt 1.4 Invite, expect ~6.8 L/100km (city) and ~4.9 L/100km (highway), or ~48 mpg UK combined. Real-world mixed driving typically returns 45–50 mpg (UK), depending on condition and driving style. MIVEC helps optimize low-load efficiency.",
