                    text: "The 4D55 powered the L200/Fortuna (1980–1995), Pajero/Shogun (1983–1991), Delica L300 (1986–1994), and early Challenger prototypes (1991–1992). All are longitudinal applications in 2.3L turbo-diesel variants. It was replaced by the 4D56 in most markets after 1991.",
