                    text: "Top issues include turbocharger bearing failure (early builds), Bosch VE injection pump wear, valve clearance drift, and glow plug system faults. These are documented in Mitsubishi service bulletins ENG‑03‑012 and TIS maintenance advisories. Most are preventable with proper servicing.",
