                    text: "The 4G63 (SOHC 8V) is mechanically robust and simple to repair. Its main risks are timing belt failure and distributor gear wear in neglected examples. With regular oil changes, ignition checks, and timely belt replacement, it can exceed 300,000 km in commercial use. Parts availability remains strong in heritage markets.",
