                    "@type": "Answer",
                    text: "The 3.5L DOHC V6 appeared in the Pajero/Shogun (1993–2006), Diamante (1993–2005), and Galant VR-4 (1994–1996). It was also used by Hyundai in the Grandeur XG (1999–2005) under OEM licensing. Later models meet Euro 3 standards.",
